com.stormpath.sdk.provider
Interface ProviderAccountRequest

public interface ProviderAccountRequest

Represents an attempt to get or create a Provider-based Account record in Stormpath.

NOTE: A Provider-specific Directory must previously exist in Stormpath and it must also be an Enabled Account Store within the Application.

Since:
1.0.beta
